.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5m10-3a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v9a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-9a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5M15 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-1 0v3a.5.5 0 0 0 1 0z" fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div><div class="paragraph-small">Audience</div></div><div class="spacer-xxxsmall"></div><div class="input-standard-container"><div class="position-relative"><input class="input-standard min-width-100-percent" data-id="audience-text" maxlength="100" placeholder="e.g. Employees of a successful startup" type="text"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="text-color-grey-600"><p class="label-regular" data-id="legal-text">By using this service, you confirm that you have all necessary rights, licenses, and permissions to upload or generate content, and that your use of any generated videos will comply with the <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%2254a83c86-f204-ad1f-448c-16190bbe66c6%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%22a27064bc-2008-0c35-de30-2b376dddae8a%22%7D%2C%7B%22componentId%22%3A%22dd1986e5-49d3-32b6-34d0-73bca0ce8c19%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%22f98b47d0-84a6-36ad-d750-650f2ffa98fb%22%7D%5D" data-wf-element-id="dd1986e5-49d3-32b6-34d0-73bca0ce8d8a" data-wf-native-id-path="a27064bc-2008-0c35-de30-2b376dddae8a:f98b47d0-84a6-36ad-d750-650f2ffa98fb:dd1986e5-49d3-32b6-34d0-73bca0ce8d8a" href="https://www.synthesia.io/legal/acceptable-use-policy" target="_blank">Acceptable Use Policy</a> and applicable regulations related to intellectual property and data privacy.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="text-align-center"><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div><div class="label-regular text-color-grey-200">No credit card required</div></div></div></aividgen-widget><div aria-hidden="true" class="sr-only" data-id="widgetcfg" data-nosnippet="" data-type="list" translate="no"><div data-code="idea-20260129-onboarding" data-type="object"><div data-key="label">Create a short, friendly onboarding welcome video for a new team member.</div></div><div data-code="idea-20260129-dog" data-type="object"><div data-key="label">A photorealistic cinematic video of a happy golden Labrador retriever running toward the camera across a sunlit grassy park.</div></div><div data-code="idea-20260129-marketing" data-type="object"><div data-key="label">Create a promotional marketing video for a fictional productivity tool called Synergy Flow.</div></div><div data-code="idea-20260129-cavern" data-type="object"><div data-key="label">An adventurous scene deep inside a massive ice cavern where explorers run with flickering torches, their warm light bouncing chaotically off translucent frozen walls. The camera follows from behind, revealing layers of stratified ice, embedded air bubbles, and glacial blue gradients.</div></div><div data-code="idea-20260129-training" data-type="object"><div data-key="label">Create a short training video that explains fundamentals of creating and maintaining secure passwords.</div></div><div data-code="idea-20260129-alley" data-type="object"><div data-key="label">A dense, atmospheric night scene in a neon-lit Chinatown alley during a torrential downpour. The camera glides forward at ground level, catching the shimmering reflections of magenta, cyan, and amber holographic signs rippling across slick pavement.</div></div></div></section><div class="display-contents hide-mobile-landscape is-active" data-id="bg-work"><div class="overflow-hidden" video-component=""><video autoplay="true" class="html-video lazy" data-poster="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/69b2ba9c4bd4a9d420a1642c_work-top-left-poster-temp.webp" id="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="true" style=""><img loading="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/69b2ba9c4bd4a9d420a1642c_work-top-left-poster-temp.webp" title="Your browser does not support the &lt;video&gt; tag"/><source data-src="https://webcdn.synthesia.io/widgets/ai-video-generator/bg-videos/work-