</style></div></div></section><section class="padding-vertical padding-xhuge" data-id="feature-tabs-section"><div class="page-padding z-1"><div class="container-large"><div class="position-relative"><div class="text-align-center"><div class="caption border-indigo-300" color="" is-round="true"><div class="caption-medium">MORE FEATURES</div></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div><h2 class="heading-large text-color-base-dark">Your full AI video toolkit</h2><div class="spacer-small"></div><div class="rich-text-large w-richtext"><p>Create high-quality videos from a script directly in your browser, within a platform built to manage your whole video workflow.</p></div></div><div class="spacer-xxxlarge"></div><div class="border-radius-large background-indigo is-100"><div class="padding-xxsmall"><div class="grid-12col-base gap-075rem w-tabs" data-current="Tab 1" data-duration-in="200" data-duration-out="200" data-easing="ease-in-out" shuffle-tabs="tab-block"><div class="flex-vertical flex-gap-1rem w-tab-menu" id="w-node-a59a2249-afdc-4ace-c7ba-102e0f776cc6-0f776cb7" section="how-to" shuffle-tabs="menu-wrapper"><a class="features-tab_link-wrap w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" data-w-tab="Tab 1" target="how-to-step"><div class="flex-horizontal gap-1rem"><div class="marketing-icon is-small is-indigo"><img alt="" class="icon-18" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/661f8cb54855cdf79a9669c1_Person-Grey.svg"/></div><div><h3 class="heading-tiny text-color-base-dark">Customizable avatars</h3><div data-id="active-tab-content"><div class="spacer-xxsmall"></div><p class="paragraph-small" target="item-description">Prompt avatars to talk in any environment and outfit. Then prompt them to act—powered by Veo 3.</p><div class="spacer-small show-tablet"></div></div></div></div></a><a class="features-tab_link-wrap w-inline-block w-tab-link" data-w-tab="Tab 2" target="how-to-step"><div class="flex-horizontal gap-1rem"><div class="marketing-icon is-small is-indigo"><img alt="" class="icon-18" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/6931668e1644662eb1a5942c_Interactivity.svg"/></div><div><h3 class="heading-tiny text-color-base-dark">Interactivity</h3><div data-id="active-tab-content"><div class="spacer-xxsmall"></div><p class="paragraph-small" target="item-description">Make your videos 10x more engaging with interactive elements such as quizzes, CTAs, and branching scenarios.</p><div class="spacer-small show-tablet"></div></div></div></div></a><a class="features-tab_link-wrap w-inline-block w-tab-link" data-w-tab="Tab 3" target="how-to-step"><div class="flex-horizontal gap-1rem"><div class="marketing-icon is-small is-indigo"><img alt="" class="icon-18" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/661f8cb9788de4ac91a1338c_ShareNetwork-Grey.svg"/></div><div><h3 class="heading-tiny text-color-base-dark">Live collaboration</h3><div data-id="active-tab-content"><div class="spacer-xxsmall"></div><p class="paragraph-small" target="item-description">Invite colleagues to share feedback and create videos together, in real-time.</p><div class="spacer-small show-tablet"></div></div></div></div></a><a class="features-tab_link-wrap w-inline-block w-tab-link" data-w-tab="Tab 4" target="how-to-step"><div class="flex-horizontal gap-1rem"><div class="marketing-icon is-small is-indigo"><img alt="" class="icon-18" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/661f8cb9c21b5248001e93f6_LineSegments-Grey.svg"/></div><div><h3 class="heading-tiny text-color-base-dark">Analytics</h3><div data-id="active-tab-content"><div class="spacer-xxsmall"></div><p class="paragraph-small" target="item-description">Understand how users interact with your videos by tracking views, watch time, engagement, and clicks.</p><div class="spacer-small show-tablet"></div></div></div></div></a><a class="features-tab_link-wrap w-inline-block w-tab-link" data-w-tab="Tab 5"><div class="flex-horizontal gap-1rem"><div class="marketing-icon is-small is-indigo"><img alt="" class="icon-18" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/661f8cb030f8300019e1a1a6_Palette-Grey.svg"/></div><div><h3 class="heading-tiny text-color-base-dark">Brand kit</h3><div data-id="active-tab-content"><div class="spacer-xxsmall"></div><p class="paragraph-small" target="item-description">Automatically apply your brand colors, fonts, logos and preferred avatars to any video you create.</p><div class="spacer-small show-tablet"></div></div></div></div></a></div><div class="border-radius-large shadow-low w-tab-content" id="w-node-a59a2249-afdc-4ace-c7ba-102e0f776d03-0f776cb7" shuffle-tabs="content-wrapper"><div class="feature-tab_pane-wrap w-tab-pane w--tab-active" data-w-tab="Tab 1"><div class="background-image-container hide-tablet"><img alt="" class="background-cover-image" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg 799w"/></div><div><div class="border-radius-large shadow-low"><div class="position-relative"><div class="overflow-hidden" video-component=""><video autoplay="true" class="html-video lazy" data-poster="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/6915ef6acd1ba77fceef1584_customizable-avatar-poster.webp" id="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="true" style=""><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/6915ef6acd1ba77fceef1584_customizable-avatar-poster.webp" title="Your browser does not support the &lt;video&gt; tag"/><source data-src="https://webcdn.synthesia.io/all-features/customizable-avatar.mp4" switch-src="" type="video/mp4"/></video></div></div></div></div></div><div class="feature-tab_pane-wrap w-tab-pane" data-w-tab="Tab 2"><div class="background-image-container hide-tablet"><img alt="" class="background-cover-image" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg 799w"/></div><div class="border-radius-large shadow-low"><div class="position-relative"><div class="overflow-hidden" video-component=""><video autoplay="true" class="html-video lazy" data-poster="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/685914977508e794c665e1dd_bento-video-buttons.webp" id="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="true" style=""><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/685914977508e794c665e1dd_bento-video-buttons.webp" title="Your browser does not support the &lt;video&gt; tag"/><source data-src="" switch-src="" type="video/mp4"/></video></div></div></div></div><div class="feature-tab_pane-wrap w-tab-pane" data-w-tab="Tab 3"><div class="background-image-container hide-tablet"><img alt="" class="background-cover-image" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg 799w"/></div><div class="border-radius-large shadow-low"><div class="position-relative"><div class="overflow-hidden" video-component=""><video autoplay="true" class="html-video lazy" data-poster="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/6697b5212f303fd3e18eee74_Live-Collab.webp" id="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="true" style=""><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/6697b5212f303fd3e18eee74_Live-Collab.webp" title="Your browser does not support the &lt;video&gt; tag"/><source data-src="https://webcdn.synthesia.io/all-features/live-collaboration.mp4" switch-src="" type="video/mp4"/></video></div></div></div></div><div class="feature-tab_pane-wrap w-tab-pane" data-w-tab="Tab 4"><div class="background-image-container hide-tablet"><img alt="" class="background-cover-image" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg 799w"/></div><div class="border-radius-large shadow-low"><div class="position-relative"><div class="overflow-hidden" video-component=""><video autoplay="true" class="html-video lazy" data-poster="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/67cb2cb9aaf603092ac232b8_Analytics.webp" id="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="true" style=""><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/67cb2cb9aaf603092ac232b8_Analytics.webp" title="Your browser does not support the &lt;video&gt; tag"/><source data-src="https://webcdn.synthesia.io/all-features/Analitycs.mp4" switch-src="" type="video/mp4"/></video></div></div></div></div><div class="feature-tab_pane-wrap w-tab-pane" data-w-tab="Tab 5"><div class="background-image-container hide-tablet"><img alt="" class="background-cover-image" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/68c96afd296b593164aa9ae7_feature-card-bg-1.jpg 799w"/></div><div class="border-radius-large shadow-low"><div class="position-relative"><div class="overflow-hidden" video-component=""><video autoplay="true" class="html-video lazy" data-poster="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/6697b51fafcf09e77cdefad1_Brand-Kit.webp" id="" loop="" muted="" playsinline="true" style=""><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/6697b51fafcf09e77cdefad1_Brand-Kit.webp" title="Your browser does not support the &lt;video&gt; tag"/><source data-src="" switch-src="" type="video/mp4"/></video></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="component-code"><div class="css w-embed"><style>
.features-tab_link-wrap {
	transition-property: box-shadow, background-color;
	transition-duration: .3s;
}
.features-tab_link-wrap [data-id="active-tab-content"] {
	overflow: hidden;
	transition: max-height .3s ease;
}
.features-tab_link-wrap:not(.w--current) [data-id="active-tab-content"] {
	max-height: 0rem;
  height: auto;
}
.features-tab_link-wrap.w--current [data-id="active-tab-content"] {
	max-height: 10rem;
  height: auto;
}
.feature-tab_pane-wrap.w--tab-active {
	display: flex;
	justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 991px) {
	.features-tab_link-wrap.w--current .flex-horizontal {
		flex-direction: column;
		grid-row-gap: .75rem;
	}
}


.features-tab_link-wrap:after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: 0rem;
  right: 0rem;
  top: -.5rem;
  pointer-events: none;
  transition: border-color .3s ease;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--indigo-200);
}
.features-tab_link-wrap:first-of-type:after,
.features-tab_link-wrap:hover:after,
.features-tab_link-wrap.w--current:after,
.features-tab_link-wrap:hover + .features-tab_link-wrap:after,
.features-tab_link-wrap.w--current + .features-tab_link-wrap:after {
	border-color: transparent;
}

/*Hide clones*/
[shuffle-tabs="menu-wrapper"] div[data-w-tab] {
  display: none;
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 991px) {
  /*Hide original tab pane*/
  [shuffle-tabs="content-wrapper"] {
    display: none;
  }
  /*Display active clone*/
  [shuffle-tabs="menu-wrapper"] a.w--current > div[data-w-tab] {
    display: block !important;
  }
}

</style></div><div class="javascript w-embed w-script"><script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
  const CLONE_QUERY = window.matchMedia('(max-width: 991px)'); // cloning breakpoint

  // Section scope
  const section = document.querySelector('[data-id="feature-tabs-section"]');
  if (!section) return;

  // Helper – initialise any <video class="lazy"> inside a node using the global lazy loader
  function initLazyVideosIn(node) {
    if (!node || !window.initLazyVideo) return;
    if (!node.querySelectorAll) return;

    var vids = node.querySelectorAll('video.lazy');
    vids.forEach(function (v) {
      window.initLazyVideo(v);
    });
  }

  // -----------------------------
  // Clone slides for mobile rearrangement
  // -----------------------------
  function rearrangeTabs() {
    // Only clone on mobile
    if (!CLONE_QUERY.matches) return;

    const wrappers = section.querySelectorAll('[shuffle-tabs="tab-block"]');
    if (!wrappers.length) return;

    wrappers.forEach((wrapper) => {
      const menuWrapper = wrapper.querySelector('[shuffle-tabs="menu-wrapper"]');
      if (!menuWrapper) return;

      const tabs = menuWrapper.querySelectorAll('a[data-w-tab]');
      const contents = wrapper.querySelectorAll('div[data-w-tab]');

      contents.forEach((content) => {
        const tabId = content.getAttribute('data-w-tab');
        const correspondingTab = [...tabs].find(
          (tab) => tab.getAttribute('data-w-tab') === tabId
        );
        if (!correspondingTab) return;

        // Remove extra clones beyond the first, if any
        const existingClones = correspondingTab.querySelectorAll(
          `div[data-w-tab="${tabId}"]`
        );
        existingClones.forEach((clone, index) => {
          if (index > 0) clone.remove();
        });

        // If one already exists inside the tab link, skip
        if (correspondingTab.querySelector(`div[data-w-tab="${tabId}"]`)) {
          return;
        }

        const contentCopy = content.cloneNode(true);
        contentCopy.removeAttribute('id');
        contentCopy.querySelectorAll('[id]').forEach((child) =>
          child.removeAttribute('id')
        );
        contentCopy.setAttribute('data-cloned', tabId);

        // Always append as last child
        correspondingTab.append(contentCopy);

        // Attach global lazy IntersectionObserver to any cloned videos
        initLazyVideosIn(contentCopy);
      });
    });
  }

  // Run cloning once on load (if under breakpoint)
  rearrangeTabs();

  // Re-run cloning when crossing into the mobile breakpoint
  CLONE_QUERY.addEventListener('change', (e) => {
    if (e.matches) {
      rearrangeTabs();
    }
  });
});
</script></div></div></section><section class="padding-vertical padding-huge" data-id="faq-section"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-large"><div class="grid-12col-base"><div class="text-align-left is-center-tablet" id="w-node-b3a70f02-3530-788e-5b14-af8bfc9a0b2d-fc9a0b29"><div class="caption border-indigo-300" color="" is-round="true"><div class="caption-medium">FAQs</div></div><div class="spacer-xxsmall"></div><h2 class="heading-large text-color-base-dark">Script to video FAQs</h2><div class="spacer-xlarge show-tablet"></div></div><div class="flex-vertical flex-gap-1rem" id="w-node-c945ec2a-0c79-9a9d-ddc6-a04d99daebb3-fc9a0b29"><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>What is the best AI script to video tool?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>Synthesia stands out as the best script to video maker because it automatically turns your script into a complete video with visuals, avatars, animations, and voiceovers. You can then customize every element — swap avatars, use your own personal avatar, adjust voices, and even generate b-roll with Veo 3 and Sora 2 directly in the editor, for free. You do not need any video editing skills or experience — Synthesia is as easy to use as PowerPoint. It’s also built for collaboration, allowing you to co-create and manage videos with your team easily. Plus, Synthesia supports instant translation into any language and runs on a secure, enterprise-grade platform.</p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>Is the script to video maker free?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>Yes, you can use Synthesia’s script to video maker for free to create videos directly in your browser. You’ll be able to generate videos from text, customize avatars, voices, visuals, and animations — all without needing video editing experience.</p><p>You can embed videos for free, or upgrade to download them in full HD and unlock premium features like interactivity, brand kits, and advanced export options.</p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>How can I turn a script into a reel or vertical video?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>Creating a vertical video is simple in Synthesia. Just write or paste your script in the AI Video Assistant, and then choose a template in the 9:16 aspect ratio. The AI will automatically generate a visually engaging video with avatars, animations, and voiceovers optimized for mobile viewing.</p><p>Alternatively, from the editor select the hamburger menu, navigate to ‘Video size’ and then select your desired size: Portrait video (9:16) for IG reels, TikToks and Stories, Square video (1:1) for LinkedIn, IG posts, X, Tall video (4:5) for tall IG posts, and Wide video (5:4) for LinkedIn, IG posts and X.</p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>Can I edit or update my video after it’s been created?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>Yes. You can easily change the script, swap avatars, or generate new visuals without re-recording anything, making content updates fast and scalable.</p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>What formats can I export my videos in?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>Synthesia videos are exported in MP4 format, which works seamlessly across most platforms. For e-learning, SCORM exports are available for LMS integration, and XLIFF exports let you translate video scripts efficiently. Enterprise plans may unlock additional export options based on your needs. Every video can be easily embedded on your website or shared externally.</p><p>All plans include Full HD (1080p) exports, with 4K available for enterprise users.</p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>What makes a good video script?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>A good video script has a clear goal, a defined audience, and a strong structure that makes it easier for your video to engage and convert.</p><p>It should start with a hook to grab attention quickly, then move to a compelling message or solution, support that with proof or examples, and conclude with a clear call‑to‑action.</p><p>Keep the language conversational and the timing smooth (about 130–150 spoken words per minute), so that narration feels natural and pacing doesn’t lose viewers.</p><p>Finally, map visuals and audio side‑by‑side (e.g. using a two-column format). This ensures that what viewers see matches what they hear and makes the final video more coherent.</p><p>See our guide on <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad2f" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad2f" href="https://www.synthesia.io/post/how-to-write-a-video-script">how to write a video script</a>, or use the <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad32" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad32" href="https://www.synthesia.io/features/ai-script-generator">AI script generator.</a></p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>How else can I generate videos with Synthesia?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>As well as uploading a script, Synthesia offers multiple AI-powered methods to create videos from various content sources. You can upload <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad39" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad39" href="https://www.synthesia.io/powerpoint-to-video">PowerPoint presentations</a>, <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad3c" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad3c" href="https://www.synthesia.io/tools/pdf-to-video">PDFs</a>, Word documents, or text files directly, and the platform will automatically transform them into professional videos. Additionally, you can paste a website URL to <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad3f" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad3f" href="https://www.synthesia.io/tools/url-to-video">convert existing web content into video</a> format, or simply describe your video idea in a few words and let the AI generate both the script and video from your prompt.</p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-wrapper"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="text-color-base-dark"><h3 class="paragraph-large is-medium" faq="question"><strong>Is it safe for businesses to create AI videos with Synthesia?</strong></h3></div><div class="text-color-indigo-500"><div class="icon-16 w-embed"><svg fill="none" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 16 17" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M8 15.2305L8 1.89714" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
<path d="M2.54688 7.34961L8.00142 1.89506L13.456 7.34961" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.8"></path>
</svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="rich-text-medium w-richtext" faq="answer"><p>Yes, Synthesia is safe for businesses and designed with enterprise-grade security in mind. The platform is SOC 2 Type II and GDPR compliant, with strict data privacy and protection measures in place. AI and human moderation, combined with a strong ethical AI policy, ensure videos are created responsibly. You fully own the videos you create and can use them commercially for training, marketing, or internal communications.</p></div><div class="spacer-xsmall"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="script-faq-schema w-embed w-script"><script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {

  // ── Schema ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  const faqRows = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-accordion-wrapper');

  if (faqRows.length > 0) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-grid .w-condition-invisible').forEach(el => el.remove());

    const data = {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      mainEntity: [],
    };

    faqRows.forEach(row => {
      const questionEl = row.querySelector("[faq='question']");
      const answerEl   = row.querySelector("[faq='answer']");
      if (!questionEl || !answerEl) return;
      data.mainEntity.push({
        "@type": "Question",
        name: questionEl.textContent,
        acceptedAnswer: {
          "@type": "Answer",
          text: answerEl.textContent,
        },
      });
    });

    const schemaScript = document.createElement('script');
    schemaScript.type = 'application/ld+json';
    schemaScript.textContent = JSON.stringify(data);
    document.head.appendChild(schemaScript);
  }

  // ── Accordion ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  faqRows.forEach((card, index) => {
    const cardHeader = card.querySelector('.faq-accordion-header');
    if (!cardHeader) return;
    card.classList.add(index === 0 ? 'is-open' : 'is-closed');
    cardHeader.addEventListener('click', () => {
      card.classList.toggle('is-open');
      card.classList.toggle('is-closed');
    });
  });

});
</script></div></div></div></section><section class="background-indigo is-100"><div class="padding-vertical padding-huge"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-large"><div class="grid-12col-base row-gap-0rem"><div id="w-node-_3d6a96a3-b892-e004-376e-e4b3c5d2565f-c5d2565a"><div class="caption border-indigo-300" color="" is-round="true"><div class="caption-medium">#1 AI VIDEO TOOL</div></div><div class="spacer-xxsmall"></div></div><div class="text-color-base-dark" id="w-node-_3d6a96a3-b892-e004-376e-e4b3c5d25663-c5d2565a"><h2 class="heading-large">Not just a script to video converter</h2><div class="spacer-small show-tablet"></div></div><div class="rich-text-large w-richtext" id="w-node-_3d6a96a3-b892-e004-376e-e4b3c5d25667-c5d2565a"><p>Synthesia is the all-in-one AI video platform for creating effective videos without expensive production methods. From <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad4c" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad4c" href="https://www.synthesia.io/features/ai-video-generator">generating bespoke b-roll</a> using the latest AI models, to creating your own <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad4f" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad4f" href="https://www.synthesia.io/features/custom-avatar/personal">personal avatar</a> to present your script, and <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad52" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad52" href="https://www.synthesia.io/features/video-translator">translating videos</a> into 160+ languages with 1-click, Synthesia speeds up video creation while reducing cost.</p><p>Create, translate, and scale video production with Synthesia.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="padding-vertical padding-xxxlarge" data-id="cross-linking-component"><div class="component-code"><div class="css w-embed"><style>
