</svg></div></div></a></div><div class="w-locales-item" role="listitem"><a class="footer_dropdown-locale-list-item-wrapper w-inline-block" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b411cc0-d8eb-7473-0eb3-1417d671f29a%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%223a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69%22%7D%5D" data-wf-element-id="5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459ad65" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69:5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459ad65_instance-4" href="/pt-br" hreflang="pt-BR"><div class="flex flex-gap_05rem flex-centre-align"><div class="paragraph-medium is-medium is-capitalized" lang-code="">pt-BR</div><div class="paragraph-medium is-medium" lang-name="">Português (Brasil)</div></div><div class="text-color-indigo-300"><div class="icon-12 w-embed"><svg aria-hidden="true" fill="none" height="100%" preserveaspectratio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" viewbox="0 0 12 12" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M11.25 2.25L4.25 9.24969L0.75 5.75" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="0.9"></path>
</svg></div></div></a></div></div></div></nav></div><div class="max-width-37rem"><div class="text-align-left is-center-tablet"><p class="paragraph-small">Synthesia is a #1 AI Video Platform for Business. Our <a data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b411cc0-d8eb-7473-0eb3-1417d671f29a%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%223a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69%22%7D%5D" data-wf-element-id="5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459ad72" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69:5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459ad72" href="/features/ai-video-generator">AI Video Generator</a> enables anyone to create professional videos without mics, cameras, actors, or studios.<br/><br/>Using AI, we’re radically changing the process of video content creation, making it scalable and affordable while maintaining high quality.</p></div></div><div class="flex-child-stretch"><div class="opacity-20"><div class="divider" color="" vertical="false"></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-gap-1-5rem"><a aria-label="Read about our security policy" class="footerv2_badge-link w-inline-block" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b411cc0-d8eb-7473-0eb3-1417d671f29a%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%223a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69%22%7D%5D" data-wf-element-id="5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459ad7c" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69:5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459ad7c" href="https://security.synthesia.io/" target="_blank"><img alt="Synthesia is SOC2 compliant" class="footerv2_aicpa-badge" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0d710/65e89895c5a4b8d764c0de36_21972-312_SOC_NonCPA.png"/></a><a aria-label="Read about our ethics policy" class="footerv2_badge-link w-inline-block" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b411cc0-d8eb-7473-0eb3-1417d671f29a%22%2C%22instan