dcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459adf8" href="https://help.synthesia.io/en/articles/7182166-how-to-contact-us#h_105ad09a88" target="_blank">Contact Sales</a><a class="paragraph-small" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b411cc0-d8eb-7473-0eb3-1417d671f29a%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%223a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69%22%7D%5D" data-wf-element-id="5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459adfa" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69:5834ca98-ddcd-32c3-f6d6-9632f459adfa" href="/partners/affiliates">Affiliates</a><a class="paragraph-small" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b411cc0-d8eb-7473-0eb3-1417d671f29a%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%223a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69%22%7D%5D" data-wf-element-id="3612fb9a-fe29-1340-d68a-de79c6e8a35f" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69:3612fb9a-fe29-1340-d68a-de79c6e8a35f" href="/partners">Partners</a><a class="paragraph-small" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b411cc0-d8eb-7473-0eb3-1417d671f29a%22%2C%22instanceId%22%3A%223a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69%22%7D%5D" data-wf-element-id="cb9e84d9-800a-946a-0eb3-920e645ad8fe" data-wf-native-id-path="3a727070-d01f-7f45-1a18-d29f89f6ad69:cb9e84d9-800a-946a-0eb3-920e645ad8fe" href="/sitemap">Sitemap</a></div></div><div class="hide-tablet"><div class="padding-top padding-xxlarge"><div class="padding-bottom padding-small"><div class="opacity-20"><div class="divider" color="" vertical="false"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-space-between is-vertical-tablet flex-gap-1-5rem"><p class="label-regular">© 2026 Synthesia Limited. All rights reserved.</p><div class="footerv2_social-wrapper"><a aria-label="Follow us on Twitter" class="w-inline-block" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-component-context="%5B%7B%22componentId%22%3A%227b41